[Kim Wooju softly] Okay, tatahimik na ako.

00:22:05.971 --> 00:22:07.681
Manahimik ka, Meri.

00:22:07.765 --> 00:22:08.891
[Meri softly] Hindi ako nakagalaw!

00:22:08.974 --> 00:22:10.017
[Tumahimik si Kim Wooju]

00:22:10.684 --> 00:22:12.144
BAHAY NI SUNDOL

